### TaskFlow Pro - REST Client API Requests (Complete Exhaustive Suite)
### VS Code REST Client Extension

### ─── Variables ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
# Run "Login - Valid User 1 (Manager)" first to populate these
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@projectId = YOUR_PROJECT_ID_HERE
@taskId = YOUR_TASK_ID_HERE
@commentId = YOUR_COMMENT_ID_HERE

# Second user token to test RBAC properties
@user2Token = YOUR_USER2_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### =========================================================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### A-01: Register new user (Happy Path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Manager User 1",
  "email": "manager1@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### A-02: Register - duplicate email
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Duplicate User",
  "email": "manager1@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}
# Expect 409 CONFLICT

### A-03: Register - invalid email
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}
# Expect 400 Validation Error

### A-04: Register - weak password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane2@example.com",
  "password": "weak"
}
# Expect 400 Validation Error

### Registar Second User (For RBAC tests)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Member User 2",
  "email": "member2@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### A-05: Login - valid credentials (User 1 - Manager)
# @name loginUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "manager1@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### Login - valid credentials (User 2 - Member)
# @name loginUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "member2@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### A-06: Login - wrong password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "manager1@example.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword!123"
}
# Expect 401 UNAUTHORIZED

### A-07: Login - unknown email
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nobody@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}
# Expect 401 UNAUTHORIZED

### A-09: Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### A-10: Refresh - invalid token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "garbage-token-xyz"
}
# Expect 401 UNAUTHORIZED

### A-12: Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### =========================================================================
### 2. USER ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### U-01: Get current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### U-02: Get current user — no auth
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
# Expect 401 UNAUTHORIZED

### U-03: Update profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Manager User Updated",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar1.jpg"
}

### U-04: Update profile - validation error
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": ""
}
# Expect 400

### U-05: Change password - valid
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "currentPassword": "SecurePass123!",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass123!"
}

### U-06: Change password - wrong current
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "currentPassword": "WrongPass123!",
  "newPassword": "AnotherPass123!"
}
# Expect 401 UNAUTHORIZED

### Revert Password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "currentPassword": "NewSecurePass123!",
  "newPassword": "SecurePass123!"
}


### =========================================================================
### 3. PROJECT ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### P-01: Create project
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "E2E API Test Project",
  "description": "Comprehensive testing project",
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### P-02: Create project — no auth
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "No Auth Project"
}
# Expect 401

### P-03: Create project — missing name
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "Missing title"
}
# Expect 400

### P-04: List projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-05: List projects — filter status
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-06: List projects — pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?page=0&size=2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-07: Get project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-08: Get project — non-member private
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}
# Expect 403 FORBIDDEN

### P-09: Get project — not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
# Expect 404 NOT_FOUND

### P-10: Update project
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Updated E2E Test Project",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### P-14: Add member (user2@example.com)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "member2@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

### P-15: Add member - already added
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "member2@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}
# Expect 409 CONFLICT

### P-17: Get members
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-11: Update project — non-manager
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Member trying to update name"
}
# Expect 403 (User 2 is MEMBER, not MANAGER)

### P-12: Archive project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-13: Archived hidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
# Should not return the archived project (until un-archived)


### =========================================================================
### 4. TASK ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

# Reactivate Project First
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### T-01: Create task
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "API Edge Case Task",
  "description": "Task created for testing edge cases",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "TODO",
  "tags": ["api", "testing"]
}

### T-02: Create Task - non-member
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer garbage-user-token-xyz
# Expect 401/403

### T-03: Create task — missing title
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "priority": "HIGH"
}
# Expect 400

### T-04: List tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### T-05: Filter tasks by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks?status=TODO
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### T-07: Get task by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### T-08: Update task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Updated API Edge Case Task",
  "priority": "CRITICAL"
}

### T-10: Status update — valid
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### T-11: Status update — invalid transition
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "TODO"
}
# Valid is IN_PROGRESS -> REVIEW or DONE. Expect 422 INVALID_STATUS_TRANSITION

### T-14: Get my tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/my-tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ST-01: Add subtask
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/subtasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Write unit tests"
}

### ST-04: Toggle subtask completion
# Replace SUBTASK_ID_HERE after running ST-01 and noting the id
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/subtasks/SUBTASK_ID_HERE/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### TT-01: Log time on a task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/time
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "hours": 2.5
}

### AT-01: Upload attachment (multipart)
# Uncomment and adjust path for manual testing
# POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/attachments
# Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
# --boundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.pdf"
# Content-Type: application/pdf
# (binary file content here)
# --boundary--

### AT-03: List attachments
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/attachments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =========================================================================
### 5. COMMENT ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### C-01: Add comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Initial comment content"
}

### C-03: Add comment - empty content
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": ""
}
# Expect 400 (if empty string blocked) or fast failure

### C-04: Get comments
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### C-05: Edit own comment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Edited comment content"
}

### C-06: Edit another's comment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Hacked comment content"
}
# Expect 403 FORBIDDEN

### C-07: Delete own comment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =========================================================================
### 6. NOTIFICATION ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### N-01: Get notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}

### N-02: Filter unread only
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}

### N-06: Mark all as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}


### =========================================================================
### 7. ACTIVITY ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### AC-01: Get project activities
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### AC-02: Get task activities
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =========================================================================
### 8. DASHBOARD ENDPOINTS
### =========================================================================

### D-01: Get dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### D-02: Dashboard (no auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
# Expect 401 UNAUTHORIZED


### =========================================================================
### ERRORS & CLEANUP (Cross-phase)
### =========================================================================

### E-01: Malformed JSON
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "manager1@example.com"
  "password": 
# Expect 400 BAD_REQUEST

### E-02: Wrong Content-Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: text/plain

{"email": "test@test.com"}
# Expect 415 UNSUPPORTED_MEDIA_TYPE

### E-06: UUID format violation
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/not-a-valid-uuid-123
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
# Expect 400 BAD_REQUEST

### T-12: Delete task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### P-18: Remove member
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/YOUR_USER2_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
